text: Christ Yarafa (born 25 December 1966) is a former cyclist from the Central African Republic. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Central African Republic male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Central African Republic Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
